Realty Executives Associates on the Square

data.description: This cozy three-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in Oak Ridge with over 3,000 square feet is a **MUST SEE** There are three bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms with kitchen, laundry, dining, living room, and a large sunroom on the main level! The basement has a potential 4th bedroom, a second full bathroom, a fireplace, a bonus/family room, and a workshop with a ton of additional storage space. There's an uncovered deck at the back of the house and two covered porches--one at the rear (walk-out basement door) and a large covered porch at the front. Newly installed fence in the front yard with a ton of landscaping, room for gardening, and quiet, shaded areas to enjoy the outside. Freshly painted interior and new appliances that all convey with the sale. This property conveniently borders the Greenway and is centrally located for shopping & dining. The front of the home also has a concrete driveway for additional parking and off-street parking. Come see this little GEM in Oak Ridge; you won't want to miss it--showings start Aug. 25th.
